## 4. PIPELINE ARCHITECTURE ‚Äî What Is Wired vs Orphaned

### SignalGenerator.generate_signals() ‚Äî 5-Step Pipeline (from unified_monitor.py)

```
unified_monitor.py ‚Üí SignalGenerator.generate_signals()
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Step 1: _generate_regular_signals()        ‚Üí DP edge, institutional context  ‚úÖ
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Step 2: _generate_lottery_signals()         ‚Üí 0DTE from high-confidence regs  ‚úÖ
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Step 3: _apply_narrative_enrichment()       ‚Üí NarrativeAgent via Cohere       ‚úÖ
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Step 4: _apply_economic_risk_management()   ‚Üí TECalendar signal veto          ‚úÖ ‚Üê HOUSING+CPI FIRE HERE
  ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Source 1: EconCalendar (FRED: FOMC)
  ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Source 2: TECalendarScraper (TE: CPI/GDP/PPI/Housing)
  ‚îÇ   ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ EXTREME (<30min): trading_allowed=False ‚Üí return []
  ‚îÇ   ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ HIGH (<2h): confidence √ó 0.7 (trading ALLOWED)
  ‚îú‚îÄ‚îÄ Step 4.5: _apply_holistic_kill_shots()      ‚Üí Trap Matrix vetoes              ‚úÖ
  ‚îî‚îÄ‚îÄ Step 5: _apply_master_filters()             ‚Üí threshold + dedup               ‚úÖ
```

### ORPHANED from Live Pipeline

| Module | File | Problem |
|--------|------|---------|
| `ReleaseDetector` | `enrichment/apis/release_detector.py` | Only called from API endpoint ‚Äî **never invoked by unified_monitor** |
| `KillChainEngine` | `enrichment/apis/kill_chain_engine.py` | Only called from `backend/api/v1/killchain.py` ‚Äî 5-layer scan does NOT feed SignalGenerator |
| `FedShiftPredictor` | `agents/economic/fed_shift_predictor.py` | Only called by orphaned ReleaseDetector |

**Critical gap:** Signal veto BLOCKS signals pre-release ‚úÖ, but when data DROPS, nothing in the live pipeline DETECTS the release. Release detection is API-polling only (widget polls every 2min).

